latestIgtvVideos.title: 4 Girls On A Road Trip | Chennai - Pondicherry | #TravelVlog | #RhythmAndVi
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What happens when four girls decide to go on their first ever road trip? 
Well, it's not what you're thinking but it was one hell of a ride.
Last year, in November, my closest friends and I (whom I've been friends with for over 16 years but never taken a single trip with) decided to take a road trip from Chennai to Pondicherry and it was a trip that we will all cherish for a lifetime.
About 2 years ago, I realized music and travel were two things that kept me sane and made me happy instantly. That's when I decided to sing & travel more. Hence, the handle name on Instagram ( @RhythmAndViews ). And since this year is all about going that extra mile, here's presenting my FIRST ever Travel Vlog with my oldest friends. Hope you guys enjoy this. ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
Face shaving made easy! * 

My friend introduced me to shaving years ago and I’ve never gone back to threading because my pain tolerance has gone down further. But if you’re in two minds to shave your face or not, NO, it won’t mean your hair will grow back thicker. I promise! 

Just a few things to keep in mind:

- Make sure you don’t have any active acne on your skin or any inflammation 
- Start with an aloe Vera gel (I’m using the one by @pureelementsindia ) 
- Use a clean razor and start in the direction of hair growth at a 45 degree angle 
- Avoid using actives for at least a day after you’ve shaved your face 
- Use aloe vera gel or a non-irritating moisturiser for post-shave care 

You’ve got this! 

Save this for your next shave sesh!

* In case of sensitive skin, always consult your Dermat
and with that, have a happy weekend 🎀🫶🏼
